dataElements.name: HIS_SOCI: (G): Decision support (clinical or other)
dataElements.description: Decision support (DS) provides program and resource managers, clinicians, staff, patients, or other people with knowledge and program-specific and/or person-specific information, intelligently filtered or presented at appropriate times, to enhance health and healthcare. DS encompasses a variety of tools to enhance decision making in the program and/or clinical workflow. These tools include computerized alerts and reminders to managers, care providers, and patients; clinical guidelines; condition-specific order sets; focused patient data reports and summaries; documentation templates; diagnostic support; and contextually relevant reference information, among other tools.
